{
	"info": {
		"name": "StayEase API",
		"description": "StayEase Hotel Booking API Collection.\n\n**Execution Order:**\nRequests must be executed in the following order for variables to be auto-populated:\n\n1. **User Authentication & Registration**\n   - Register Customer → sets `customerToken`\n   - Register Hotel Manager → sets `managerToken`\n   - Register Admin → sets `adminToken`\n   - Register with Invalid Password (no dependency)\n   - Register with Invalid Email (no dependency)\n   - Login Successfully (requires customer to be registered)\n   - Login with Invalid Credentials (requires customer to be registered)\n\n2. **Hotel Management** (requires tokens from step 1)\n   - View Hotels Publicly (no dependency)\n   - Admin Create Hotel → sets `hotelId`\n   - Manager Create Hotel (Unauthorized)\n   - Manager Update Hotel (requires `hotelId`)\n   - Admin Delete Hotel (requires `hotelId`)\n   - Manager Delete Hotel (Unauthorized) (requires `hotelId`)\n\n3. **Booking Management** (requires tokens and `hotelId` from previous steps)\n   - Create Hotel with Limited Rooms → sets `hotelId` (overrides previous)\n   - Book a Room → sets `bookingId`\n   - Book When No Rooms Available (requires `hotelId`)\n   - Retrieve Booking Details (requires `bookingId`)\n   - Manager Cancel Booking (requires `bookingId`)\n   - Customer Cancel Booking (Unauthorized) (requires `bookingId`)",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "baseUrl",
			"value": "http://localhost:8081/api"
		},
		{
			"key": "customerToken",
			"value": ""
		},
		{
			"key": "managerToken",
			"value": ""
		},
		{
			"key": "adminToken",
			"value": ""
		},
		{
			"key": "hotelId",
			"value": ""
		},
		{
			"key": "bookingId",
			"value": ""
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "User Authentication & Registration",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Register Customer",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"customer@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Test@123!\",\n  \"firstName\": \"Test\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Customer\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/register",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["users", "register"]
						}
					},
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"type": "text/javascript",
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    if (jsonData.token) {",
									"        pm.collectionVariables.set('customerToken', jsonData.token);",
									"    }",
									"}"
								]
							}
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"name": "Register Hotel Manager",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"manager@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Manager@123!\",\n  \"firstName\": \"Test\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Manager\",\n  \"role\": \"HOTEL_MANAGER\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/register",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["users", "register"]
						}
					},
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"type": "text/javascript",
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    if (jsonData.token) {",
									"        pm.collectionVariables.set('managerToken', jsonData.token);",
									"    }",
									"}"
								]
							}
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"name": "Register Admin",
					"request": {
